[Tingyun Pavilion]

4
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:32,120
I also brought gifts for Miss Shei,

5
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,400
Stone, Mr. Tang,

6
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,509
and Gu Xitan.

7
00:01:34,509 --> 00:01:35,759
Foxy Tang went back to his room to rest

8
00:01:35,759 --> 00:01:37,509
after seeing Minister Tang off.

9
00:01:37,509 --> 00:01:38,479
Your Highness, why don't you

10
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:39,710
let me keep these for you?

11
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:41,000
Don't call me Your Highness.

12
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,310
Although I'm a princess now,

13
00:01:42,310 --> 00:01:44,039
I grew up in the Sword Alliance.

14
00:01:44,479 --> 00:01:45,150
Only when

15
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:45,920
I'm with you guys

16
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,180
do I feel truly at ease.

17
00:01:48,210 --> 00:01:49,490
This is my home.

18
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:51,350
Me too.

19
00:01:52,250 --> 00:01:54,009
Not until Mr. Tang took me in

20
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:55,759
and I met everyone

21
00:01:56,280 --> 00:01:58,080
did I know what a home feels like.

22
00:01:58,550 --> 00:01:59,130
Give it back!

23
00:01:59,130 --> 00:02:00,280
Why are you chasing me?

24
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,790
Xianling Herb is for making soup,

25
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:02,870
not for feeding curse bugs.

26
00:02:02,870 --> 00:02:04,600
Let me feed it to the bugs first!

27
00:02:05,190 --> 00:02:05,930
Give it back to me!

28
00:02:05,930 --> 00:02:06,560
Don't chase me!

29
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,230
If you want it,

30
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,490
go pick some yourself!

31
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:13,400
Come back!

32
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:14,470
Stop chasing me!

33
00:02:16,310 --> 00:02:17,610
Alright,
let's not talk about this anymore.

34
00:02:17,610 --> 00:02:18,870
With us here and Foxy Tang,

35
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,079
as long as we're together,

36
00:02:20,079 --> 00:02:21,240
this will always be

37
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:21,840
our home.

38
00:02:25,240 --> 00:02:26,820
Someone as strong-willed as her

39
00:02:26,820 --> 00:02:29,110
has finally stepped into a bright future.

40
00:02:29,110 --> 00:02:30,840
How could I not be happy for her?

41
00:02:31,550 --> 00:02:32,350
But...

42
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,880
she's drifting away from me.

43
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:43,079
It hurts, Senior.

44
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,520
-You always…
-It's a good thing that it hurts.

45
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,620
A promising young man like you
shouldn't belittle yourself,

46
00:02:46,620 --> 00:02:49,020
or you'll remain this way
your entire life.

47
00:02:49,430 --> 00:02:50,560
I'm not.

48
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,150
I'm just...

49
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:52,079
Speak properly.

50
00:02:52,500 --> 00:02:54,060
Don't be so bashful.

51
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:55,420
The way you look now

52
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:58,020
is what really makes you unworthy of her.

53
00:02:58,800 --> 00:02:59,570
Look at them.

54
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,280
Aside from Tang Lici,

55
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:03,240
who among them has a noble background?

56
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,370
Do they act like you?

57
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,520
Yes.

58
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:07,230
She's a princess now.

59
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:08,280
But she...

60
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:10,390
is also Ms. Zhong from the Sword Alliance.

61
00:03:10,390 --> 00:03:11,800
Your swordsmanship is so poor.

62
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:13,360
You still have the nerve
to think about this?

63
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,150
Besides,

64
00:03:15,480 --> 00:03:17,990
if she's really keeping her distance
from you because of that,

65
00:03:17,990 --> 00:03:18,940
why bother

66
00:03:19,579 --> 00:03:21,230
pursuing her?

67
00:03:25,310 --> 00:03:26,110
You're right.

68
00:03:27,960 --> 00:03:29,020
Thank you, Senior.

69
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:31,800
Good.

70
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:32,840
Go now.

71
00:03:39,329 --> 00:03:39,790
Senior.

72
00:03:40,870 --> 00:03:43,280
You seem to understand everything
so clearly.

73
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:43,940
How come...

74
00:03:44,710 --> 00:03:46,240
you still don't have a wife?

75
00:03:46,320 --> 00:03:48,050
Gu Xitan, you little brat! I...

76
00:03:48,329 --> 00:03:48,890
Zhong!

77
00:03:59,630 --> 00:04:00,480
I have to say,

78
00:04:01,020 --> 00:04:03,350
the dinner Shei made tonight was amazing.

79
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:05,030
I was about to burst.

80
00:04:05,910 --> 00:04:07,710
You're still alive, aren't you?

81
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,590
Why is it that after spending so much time

82
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,470
with Foxy Tang,

83
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:12,530
you've only picked up his bad habits?

84
00:04:19,570 --> 00:04:20,750
The Little Fox isn't here?

85
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:21,680
He went to see off the Minister Tang

86
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,480
and hasn't come back yet.

87
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,040
He's probably
slacking off somewhere again.

88
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,040
Come on, Senior.

89
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,600
I don't mean to blame you,

90
00:04:26,600 --> 00:04:27,600
but you can't just show up

91
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,800
out of nowhere

92
00:04:28,950 --> 00:04:30,720
just because I used to admire you.

93
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,270
That's so...

94
00:04:31,270 --> 00:04:32,310
Stop it.

95
00:04:32,560 --> 00:04:33,510
I, your senior,

96
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:34,970
am in a foul mood right now.

97
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:36,720
I finally made it to Mount Baojing,

98
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,180
and none of you were there—

99
00:04:41,159 --> 00:04:42,420
not even the old woman.

100
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:44,540
Who are you calling an old woman?

101
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:48,190
Whoever responds first, that's who.

102
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:48,680
You...

103
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:51,220
You don't have to be like this.

104
00:04:52,110 --> 00:04:52,970
Where is Xue Fu?

105
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:57,510
Xue Fu is so small.

106
00:04:57,830 --> 00:04:58,630
I'd like to see

107
00:04:58,630 --> 00:05:00,830
what kind of precious treasure this is.

108
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:03,800
A chicken?

109
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:08,000
My little darling Xue Fu.

110
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:11,590
Wait, wait.

111
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:12,150
Wait.

112
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,390
Xue Fu is a chicken?

113
00:05:15,070 --> 00:05:16,030
-Chicken?
-Chicken?

114
00:05:16,030 --> 00:05:17,430
-She's Xue Fu!
-She's Xue Fu!

115
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:18,870
Isn't Xue Fu a chicken?

116
00:05:19,310 --> 00:05:20,720
-Xue Fu is not a chicken.
-Xue Fu is not a chicken.

117
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,580
-Xue Fu is Xue Fu.
-Xue Fu is Xue Fu.

118
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:23,430
Shen,

119
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,270
this...

120
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:26,090
Xue Fu is not a chicken.

121
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,430
Xue Fu is Xue Fu.

122
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:28,690
Look.

123
00:05:35,670 --> 00:05:36,670
How interesting.

124
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:39,040
You two really are interesting.

125
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,510
See? I told you.

126
00:05:40,530 --> 00:05:41,730
You're the only blind one here

127
00:05:41,730 --> 00:05:43,570
who can't see how beautiful Xue Fu is.

128
00:05:43,570 --> 00:05:45,100
From the very first glance,

129
00:05:45,110 --> 00:05:47,040
I felt she was unnaturally pretty.

130
00:05:47,770 --> 00:05:49,770
Look at her fur, those little paws—

131
00:05:50,510 --> 00:05:51,310
one of a kind

132
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:52,920
in this world, got it?

133
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:56,550
Shui Duopo, I'm telling you,

134
00:05:56,550 --> 00:05:57,430
Xue Fu is just

135
00:05:57,460 --> 00:05:58,560
temporarily staying with you.

136
00:05:58,560 --> 00:06:00,690
I'll be checking on her anytime I want.

137
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,890
Your claws are dirty. Don't touch it.

138
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,630
Just one touch.

139
00:06:04,630 --> 00:06:05,560
Don't touch her!

140
00:06:09,140 --> 00:06:10,140
So cute.

141
00:06:13,690 --> 00:06:14,750
Am I the only one who doesn't see it?

142
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:15,390
So cute.

143
00:06:20,020 --> 00:06:21,550
Just one last step,

144
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,920
and I can turn back time

145
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:25,560
and rewrite fate.

146
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:28,290
You'll help me, won't you,

147
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:29,800
Brother?

148
00:06:55,390 --> 00:06:58,050
You were the crown prince
of the former dynasty?

149
00:06:58,240 --> 00:06:59,840
The chaos caused by Yique Yinyang

150
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:02,240
began because my father trusted traitors.

151
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,980
Though I was the crown prince,

152
00:07:04,030 --> 00:07:05,490
I failed to stop my father.

153
00:07:06,220 --> 00:07:07,750
I could only watch helplessly

154
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,410
as people suffered terribly.

155
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:10,780
Your Highness,

156
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,510
the rebels have taken several cities.

157
00:07:12,510 --> 00:07:13,780
His Majesty is still unconscious.

158
00:07:13,780 --> 00:07:14,840
At a time like this,

159
00:07:15,130 --> 00:07:16,120
have you really made up your mind

160
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,380
to go to Tianjing Pavilion to cultivate?

161
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,370
I can't save

162
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,280
hundreds of thousands of lives.

163
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:34,610
Therefore,

164
00:07:35,510 --> 00:07:38,159
I might as well go to Tianjing Pavilion
to cultivate.

165
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:38,870
I am,

166
00:07:39,610 --> 00:07:41,270
among all those still living,

167
00:07:41,620 --> 00:07:43,490
the one who deserves death the most.

168
00:07:43,490 --> 00:07:44,550
If I'm still alive,

169
00:07:45,320 --> 00:07:47,390
then others certainly shouldn't die.

170
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:48,920
If I cannot forgive others,

171
00:07:49,590 --> 00:07:51,060
I certainly cannot forgive myself.

172
00:07:51,060 --> 00:07:53,390
Then I must
make an agreement with you, Sir.

173
00:07:53,390 --> 00:07:55,250
We'll keep each other's secrets.

174
00:07:56,120 --> 00:07:57,200
Don't tell anyone

175
00:07:57,220 --> 00:07:58,150
about my secret,

176
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,720
and I won't tell anyone

177
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:01,120
who you really are.

178
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,330
A mistake is a mistake.

179
00:08:04,250 --> 00:08:05,870
Pain doesn't disappear

180
00:08:06,790 --> 00:08:08,590
just because you hide the truth.

181
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,560
I'm telling you,

182
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,980
this myna is really smart.

183
00:08:15,980 --> 00:08:17,830
It just called me a genius.

184
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:20,180
Are you sure it wasn't insulting you?

185
00:08:20,190 --> 00:08:20,950
How could that be an insult?

186
00:08:20,950 --> 00:08:21,510
What's going on?

187
00:08:21,510 --> 00:08:22,800
It definitely was insulting you.

188
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,130
What are you looking at?

189
00:08:26,630 --> 00:08:28,480
Mr. Chi, Senior.

190
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,970
What's so special about this bird?

191
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,809
This myna's no ordinary bird.

192
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,250
It can not only talk,

193
00:08:36,900 --> 00:08:37,380
but also

194
00:08:37,409 --> 00:08:38,240
tell a person's

195
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,240
most accurate trait

196
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:40,570
the moment it sees them.

197
00:08:41,600 --> 00:08:43,030
The most accurate trait?

198
00:08:43,510 --> 00:08:43,870
Yes.

199
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,680
Princess, Princess.

200
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,080
See?

201
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,080
Right?

202
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,960
Smart, huh?

203
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,820
This bird is really interesting.

204
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,160
What about me?

205
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,280
What about me?

206
00:08:53,670 --> 00:08:54,270
Silly dog.

207
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:55,080
Silly dog.

208
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,440
You...

209
00:08:59,090 --> 00:09:00,200
-Mr. Chi...
-I'll...

210
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:00,670
Don't be rash.

211
00:09:00,670 --> 00:09:01,720
I'll teach you a lesson!

212
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,970
Chi Yun! Chi Yun!

213
00:09:03,570 --> 00:09:08,170
When something's out of the ordinary,
there's usually something fishy behind it.

214
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,830
Master Puzhu, your leg injury

215
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:16,960
has healed already.

216
00:09:18,670 --> 00:09:19,760
It's all thanks to you,

217
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,970
Mr. Tang.

218
00:09:23,480 --> 00:09:25,000
It's all thanks to Shui Duopo's

219
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,330
superb medical skills.

220
00:09:26,350 --> 00:09:27,880
It had nothing to do with me.

221
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,590
I can tell

222
00:09:30,670 --> 00:09:32,800
you've got something on your mind too.

223
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,080
Crown prince! Crown prince!

224
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,570
Lately, there have been

225
00:09:51,590 --> 00:09:52,870
so many of these gossiping birds

226
00:09:52,870 --> 00:09:54,130
in the Sword Alliance.

227
00:09:54,670 --> 00:09:56,690
Master Puzhu, you don't get out much,

228
00:09:56,690 --> 00:09:57,620
so it's no wonder

229
00:09:57,790 --> 00:09:58,650
you don't know.

230
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:01,270
Mr. Tang,

231
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:03,310
did you come to see me early this morning

232
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:05,510
just to watch mynas leaving their nest?

233
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:07,840
Mynas

234
00:10:08,000 --> 00:10:09,860
are birds with regular patterns.

235
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,360
They leave their nests at dawn

236
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,480
and return at dusk.

237
00:10:14,150 --> 00:10:16,750
Have you received any letters
from your family

238
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,270
during these years

239
00:10:19,270 --> 00:10:20,630
at Tianjing Pavilion?

240
00:10:22,350 --> 00:10:23,180
Cultivators

241
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,370
sever their ties to family,

242
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,480
like flowers parted from their branches,

243
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,740
drifting with the wind

244
00:10:29,150 --> 00:10:31,030
and never asking where they came from.

245
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:31,830
But what if...

246
00:10:33,030 --> 00:10:34,240
your family

247
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:36,510
wants to see you?

248
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,050
Once separated,

249
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:40,670
meeting again is but a delusion.

250
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:44,150
Mr. Tang,
why do you ask these questions today?

251
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,000
I just saw birds leaving their nests

252
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,800
and felt somewhat melancholic.

253
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,910
My ties to the past were severed

254
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:55,170
the moment I entered Tianjing Pavilion.

255
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,690
But yours

256
00:10:57,800 --> 00:10:58,670
are still trapped

257
00:10:58,670 --> 00:10:59,870
in that Zhoudi Tower.

258
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:06,470
Sir, are you trying to lecture me again?

259
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,600
I heard about the Battle of Peony Pavilion

260
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,550
from Master Shao

261
00:11:10,730 --> 00:11:11,970
and Master Cheng.

262
00:11:13,170 --> 00:11:14,970
I did hold prejudice against you

263
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,390
in the past.

264
00:11:17,270 --> 00:11:18,670
Mr. Tang, your obsession

265
00:11:19,510 --> 00:11:20,770
may end up hurting you.

266
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,240
I hope you

267
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,860
can let go of your past.

268
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,240
So you're

269
00:11:29,710 --> 00:11:30,840
concerned about me?

270
00:11:35,750 --> 00:11:36,610
But perhaps...

271
00:11:38,360 --> 00:11:39,840
I need this obsession

272
00:11:40,870 --> 00:11:41,750
so I won't be

273
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:44,080
a wandering ghost.

274
00:11:56,290 --> 00:11:57,480
My injury is healed.

275
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:59,550
I'm heading down the mountain today

276
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:00,910
to lead the Sword Alliance disciples

277
00:12:00,910 --> 00:12:02,030
in investigating leads

278
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,480
on Fengliu Shop's new base

279
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:04,940
and to demolish it in time.

280
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:11,120
Then I wish you

281
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:13,340
never have to look back

282
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:14,810
on your sacred path.

283
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:30,700
Mr. Tang.

284
00:12:31,350 --> 00:12:32,150
It's nothing.

285
00:12:33,360 --> 00:12:35,220
You may go down the mountain, Sir.

286
00:12:52,830 --> 00:12:53,880
I, Xijin,

287
00:12:54,370 --> 00:12:56,600
formally invite you to Shisan Tower
for a discussion

