00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,440
You have 3 days.

290
00:13:00,050 --> 00:13:01,520
If you don't arrive by then,

291
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:02,760
I will announce

292
00:13:02,790 --> 00:13:04,550
your noble status to the world.

293
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,090
And Shisan Tower

294
00:13:06,090 --> 00:13:08,250
will share honor and disgrace with you.

295
00:13:08,250 --> 00:13:09,490
Xijin.

296
00:13:10,810 --> 00:13:11,800
Not only are you going to reveal

297
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:14,460
Master Puzhu's identity
in the former dynasty,

298
00:13:14,520 --> 00:13:15,870
but you also want to involve him

299
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:17,390
with Shisan Tower.

300
00:13:20,150 --> 00:13:21,630
Master Fang,

301
00:13:22,430 --> 00:13:24,290
you really never learn to behave.

302
00:13:26,020 --> 00:13:27,220
Restore the country?

303
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:28,120
You're trying to

304
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:30,050
drag Master Puzhu into rebellion.

305
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,000
I, Tang Lici,

306
00:13:46,330 --> 00:13:47,520
am here specifically

307
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:49,320
to visit Fang Pingzhai, the head

308
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,130
of the Fallen Shisan Tower.

309
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:18,840
Mr. Tang,

310
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,720
if I remember correctly,

311
00:14:20,750 --> 00:14:21,350
the letter

312
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,680
was meant for Master Puzhu, right?

313
00:14:24,750 --> 00:14:25,680
Master Puzhu...

314
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,770
doesn't want to see you.

315
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:31,830
That's really unfair.

316
00:14:32,670 --> 00:14:34,870
You treat me like nothing,

317
00:14:35,790 --> 00:14:37,320
yet you care so much

318
00:14:38,170 --> 00:14:39,560
for my brother,

319
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:42,330
the crown prince of the former dynasty,

320
00:14:42,330 --> 00:14:44,570
Chai Zongxun,

321
00:14:44,790 --> 00:14:47,120
now the high and mighty Master Puzhu

322
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,700
of Tianjing Pavilion,

323
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:51,840
even venturing into Shisan Tower alone
for him.

324
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,700
I have to admit,

325
00:14:52,790 --> 00:14:54,240
I'm a little jealous.

326
00:14:55,150 --> 00:14:56,960
The first time I ventured into the tower,

327
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,150
I already told you

328
00:14:58,870 --> 00:15:00,400
that being overly obsessed

329
00:15:00,480 --> 00:15:01,910
isn't a good thing.

330
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:05,840
So is being like Master Puzhu,

331
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:07,200
detached from everything,

332
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,330
really a good thing?

333
00:15:09,120 --> 00:15:10,320
Or do you really think he has

334
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:11,320
transcended worldly attachments

335
00:15:11,320 --> 00:15:12,720
and let go of everything?

336
00:15:14,390 --> 00:15:14,910
Wrong.

337
00:15:15,630 --> 00:15:16,790
He's just too ashamed

338
00:15:16,790 --> 00:15:17,910
to face his disgraceful past.

339
00:15:17,910 --> 00:15:18,910
He's avoiding it.

340
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,240
If Chai Zongxun

341
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,510
truly has a clear conscience,

342
00:15:21,510 --> 00:15:23,080
why doesn't he dare to face me?

343
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:25,150
Back then, he let the rebel army
into the city,

344
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,120
leaving the country to me,

345
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,120
an inexperienced boy,

346
00:15:27,120 --> 00:15:28,720
and then simply walked away.

347
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:30,120
Fortunately, that night

348
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:31,840
I took the advice of my old ministers

349
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:33,870
and escaped through the secret passage
with the royal treasury.

350
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:35,390
That's how I was able to found
the Fallen Shisan Tower

351
00:15:35,390 --> 00:15:36,840
and raise my loyal assassins.

352
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:37,390
Now,

353
00:15:37,910 --> 00:15:38,750
I've finally found a way

354
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:39,720
to stand under the sun again,

355
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:41,270
openly and rightfully.

356
00:15:41,430 --> 00:15:43,430
That throne has always belonged...

357
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:47,360
Kneel!

358
00:15:49,870 --> 00:15:51,290
Remnant of the former dynasty!

359
00:15:51,290 --> 00:15:52,290
Don't you realize

360
00:15:52,490 --> 00:15:53,750
who you're talking to?

361
00:15:57,790 --> 00:15:58,270
Tell me.

362
00:15:58,540 --> 00:15:59,800
Who's behind all this?

363
00:16:04,030 --> 00:16:05,360
You knew from the start

364
00:16:05,360 --> 00:16:06,720
that I could use the Rebirth Scroll.

365
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:08,580
Liu Yan would never tell you this.

366
00:16:08,830 --> 00:16:09,760
Whoever told you

367
00:16:09,920 --> 00:16:11,120
must be someone else.

368
00:16:11,450 --> 00:16:12,510
Who is this person?

369
00:16:13,880 --> 00:16:15,270
Is it Ghostly Peony?

370
00:16:18,550 --> 00:16:19,410
How about this?

371
00:16:20,050 --> 00:16:21,650
Teach me the Rebirth Scroll,

372
00:16:21,850 --> 00:16:23,450
and I'll tell you where he is.

373
00:16:31,030 --> 00:16:32,940
Mr. Tang, you truly are clever.

374
00:16:36,520 --> 00:16:38,640
This is called Inverted Dream.

375
00:16:38,890 --> 00:16:41,360
It is a magical artifact
created by Qiaoyi Qiankun,

376
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:43,120
capable of traveling to the past

377
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:45,080
and reversing time.

378
00:16:46,070 --> 00:16:47,660
It contains the power from Tianren Realm.

379
00:16:47,660 --> 00:16:49,570
It needs the Rebirth Scroll
to activate it.

380
00:16:49,570 --> 00:16:50,300
Originally,

381
00:16:50,600 --> 00:16:52,350
I asked Chai Zongxun
to come to Shisan Tower

382
00:16:52,350 --> 00:16:54,350
because I wanted him to persuade you

383
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:56,720
to activate this magical artifact for me.

384
00:16:57,250 --> 00:16:59,110
I didn't expect you to come uninvited.

385
00:16:59,110 --> 00:17:00,700
What a pleasant surprise.

386
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:02,120
Tang Lici,

387
00:17:02,480 --> 00:17:03,440
now I command you

388
00:17:03,730 --> 00:17:04,960
to use the power of the Rebirth Scroll

389
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:06,200
to activate the Inverted Dream

390
00:17:06,200 --> 00:17:07,800
and help me rewrite history.

391
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:08,970
Otherwise,

392
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,240
my men will immediately

393
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,240
announce to the world

394
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,720
that Master Puzhu is the crown prince

395
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:13,980
of the former dynasty.

396
00:17:15,550 --> 00:17:16,460
Think about it.

397
00:17:17,060 --> 00:17:18,380
If the current emperor

398
00:17:18,410 --> 00:17:19,440
learns of this,

399
00:17:20,099 --> 00:17:21,359
will he turn a blind eye

400
00:17:21,589 --> 00:17:22,510
and keep his alliance

401
00:17:22,510 --> 00:17:24,000
with the Sword Alliance

402
00:17:24,349 --> 00:17:26,030
to fight against the Fengliu Shop,

403
00:17:26,030 --> 00:17:27,400
or will he see

404
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,350
Chai Zongxun and me,

405
00:17:29,350 --> 00:17:31,120
remnants of the former dynasty,

406
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:32,510
as the greater threat?

407
00:17:33,090 --> 00:17:34,420
Then you'll have to die.

408
00:17:34,510 --> 00:17:36,310
Killing me won't do you any good.

409
00:17:37,050 --> 00:17:37,770
Wait.

410
00:18:06,710 --> 00:18:07,200
Xijin,

411
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:09,300
I'll go in with you.

412
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:12,730
Not entering Tianjing Pavilion

413
00:18:12,730 --> 00:18:15,390
and instead fighting
alongside you and Father—

414
00:18:15,810 --> 00:18:17,340
isn't that what you wanted?

415
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:22,560
That's my brother!

416
00:18:23,760 --> 00:18:24,610
Master Puzhu.

417
00:18:25,570 --> 00:18:27,330
This is my own karmic debt

418
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:29,260
and the Chai family's sin.

419
00:18:30,460 --> 00:18:32,120
If the Inverted Dream is real,

420
00:18:32,170 --> 00:18:34,230
I'll have a chance to rewrite history

421
00:18:35,190 --> 00:18:36,410
and take responsibility on the day

422
00:18:36,410 --> 00:18:37,410
of the rebellion,

423
00:18:38,070 --> 00:18:39,130
sparing the people

424
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,460
from the flames of war.

425
00:18:43,660 --> 00:18:45,320
Let's see whether this choice

426
00:18:45,550 --> 00:18:46,200
can change

427
00:18:46,990 --> 00:18:48,360
the outcome.

428
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:52,450
Can it really

429
00:18:52,820 --> 00:18:54,300
change the outcome?

430
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:00,310
I see.

431
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:08,200
Master Puzhu,

432
00:19:08,790 --> 00:19:09,790
your own karma

433
00:19:10,760 --> 00:19:12,560
should be resolved by yourself.

434
00:19:14,110 --> 00:19:14,680
I will

435
00:19:15,160 --> 00:19:17,270
activate this magical artifact for you

436
00:19:17,270 --> 00:19:18,870
and send you back to the past.

437
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,480
I've already set the time—

438
00:19:44,660 --> 00:19:46,720
the year of the Battle of Tiandu Peak.

439
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:27,630
The Inverted Dream is real.

440
00:20:29,610 --> 00:20:30,470
Your Highness!

441
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,310
Your Highness,

442
00:20:32,750 --> 00:20:33,770
you can't enter Tianjing Pavilion

443
00:20:33,770 --> 00:20:34,730
at such a time!

444
00:20:34,930 --> 00:20:36,300
The rebel army has taken several cities,

445
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,540
His Majesty is still unconscious,

446
00:20:37,540 --> 00:20:38,830
and the Imperial Preceptor
is at Tiandu Peak,

447
00:20:38,830 --> 00:20:40,450
far away and unable to return in time.

448
00:20:40,450 --> 00:20:42,090
Yet you want to enter
Tianjing Pavilion now?

449
00:20:42,090 --> 00:20:42,980
The enemy is at our gates.

450
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:44,370
Your Highness, please reconsider!

451
00:20:44,370 --> 00:20:46,050
Your Highness, I beg you

452
00:20:46,080 --> 00:20:47,210
to guard the capital

453
00:20:47,310 --> 00:20:48,710
and quell the rebellion!

454
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:50,680
Your Highness!

455
00:21:07,680 --> 00:21:08,210
Brother,

456
00:21:08,680 --> 00:21:09,720
over the years I've been sending

457
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:10,750
Shisan Tower's sworn assassins

458
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:11,830
across the land to gather intelligence

459
00:21:11,830 --> 00:21:13,030
and uncover the cause

460
00:21:13,090 --> 00:21:14,200
of this war.

461
00:21:14,820 --> 00:21:16,310
I know exactly where the main forces

462
00:21:16,310 --> 00:21:17,510
of the rebel army are

463
00:21:17,640 --> 00:21:19,030
and where they hide their supplies.

464
00:21:19,030 --> 00:21:20,240
We have a huge advantage,

465
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:21,700
enough to win this battle.

466
00:21:21,880 --> 00:21:23,200
If you stay to help me

467
00:21:23,200 --> 00:21:24,090
defend the capital

468
00:21:24,090 --> 00:21:25,260
and pin the enemy down,

469
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:26,830
I can strike under cover of night,

470
00:21:26,830 --> 00:21:28,400
slip past their front,
penetrate into their rear

471
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:29,640
to burn their provisions,

472
00:21:29,640 --> 00:21:31,300
and deal them a decisive blow.

473
00:21:34,790 --> 00:21:36,240
Will this plan end the war

474
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:37,980
and reduce casualties?

475
00:21:41,290 --> 00:21:42,220
All these years,

476
00:21:42,790 --> 00:21:45,200
I've been running simulations
of this battle every day.

477
00:21:45,200 --> 00:21:47,460
No one knows this battle better than I do,

478
00:21:47,640 --> 00:21:48,920
and no one knows better

479
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,480
how to win it.

480
00:21:55,110 --> 00:21:55,960
I promise

481
00:21:56,270 --> 00:21:57,640
I won't seek glory in battle;

482
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:59,040
I will limit the fighting

483
00:21:59,070 --> 00:22:00,470
so losses are minimized.

484
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,090
Carry out my orders:

485
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,200
dispatch 5000 elite troops immediately

486
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,560
for the Sixth Prince to command.

487
00:22:13,560 --> 00:22:15,640
Bring the civilians outside the city
into the walls for shelter.

488
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:18,170
Open the treasury for military expenses
and soldier compensation.

489
00:22:18,170 --> 00:22:19,100
Spread the word

490
00:22:19,130 --> 00:22:20,510
that His Majesty
has regained consciousness

491
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:22,350
and intends to execute
the traitor Yique Yinyang

492
00:22:22,350 --> 00:22:23,650
to uphold imperial order.

493
00:22:23,650 --> 00:22:24,910
If the rebels abandon their cause

494
00:22:24,910 --> 00:22:26,180
and surrender to the royal forces,

495
00:22:26,180 --> 00:22:27,260
they will be pardoned.

496
00:22:27,260 --> 00:22:29,000
If they persist in their rebellion,

497
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:30,510
they will face punishment.

498
00:22:30,510 --> 00:22:32,200
Meanwhile, urgently summon
the loyal forces everywhere

499
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:33,130
to aid the throne

500
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,570
and save the nation.

501
00:22:35,960 --> 00:22:37,720
Yes, Your Highness!

502
00:22:44,720 --> 00:22:45,960
Master Puzhu is truly

503
00:22:45,960 --> 00:22:47,160
a man of great talent.

504
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:48,590
However,

505
00:22:49,920 --> 00:22:51,440
when you returned to the past,

506
00:22:51,440 --> 00:22:53,030
why did you all avoid

507
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:54,640
mentioning that topic?

508
00:23:02,640 --> 00:23:03,370
Master Shao,

509
00:23:03,960 --> 00:23:05,480
during the turmoil of the former dynasty,

510
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:07,610
why didn't Yique Yinyang come to help?

511
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:09,810
Wasn't he the Imperial Preceptor?

512
00:23:09,960 --> 00:23:10,750
I've been puzzled

513
00:23:10,750 --> 00:23:12,210
about this for a long time.

514
00:23:12,510 --> 00:23:14,270
According to captured palace eunuchs,

515
00:23:14,270 --> 00:23:15,160
Yique Yinyang

516
00:23:15,160 --> 00:23:17,220
once sighted a dragon at Tiandu Peak,

517
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,200
so when the former dynasty's emperor

518
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,130
fell into a coma,

519
00:23:20,240 --> 00:23:22,170
he chose that place to pray for him.

520
00:23:22,680 --> 00:23:24,350
Tiandu Peak is far from the capital.

521
00:23:24,350 --> 00:23:25,640
When the rebel army heard the news,

522
00:23:25,640 --> 00:23:27,440
they believed the time to strike had come,

523
00:23:27,440 --> 00:23:28,510
so they called heroes
from the martial arts world

524
00:23:28,510 --> 00:23:30,070
to jointly attack Yique Yinyang

525
00:23:30,070 --> 00:23:31,440
to pin him down.

526
00:23:32,350 --> 00:23:33,680
Taking advantage of that, the rebel army

527
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:34,940
breached the capital.

528
00:23:35,830 --> 00:23:36,880
Strangely, however,

529
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:38,550
after the battle,

530
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:39,640
no signs of any ritual

531
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:41,070
were found at the site.

532
00:23:41,790 --> 00:23:43,720
According to Yique Yinyang's attendant,

533
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:44,880
he simply stood on the cliff

534
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:46,200
every day, gazing into the distance

535
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,350
and staring at the sky

536
00:23:47,350 --> 00:23:48,650
day and night without rest.

537
00:23:48,650 --> 00:23:50,420
And he wouldn't let anyone approach him,

538
00:23:50,420 --> 00:23:52,080
which was quite frightening.

539
00:23:53,310 --> 00:23:54,200
Some say

540
00:23:54,350 --> 00:23:56,550
Yique Yinyang wasn't looking at the sky

541
00:23:56,640 --> 00:23:58,040
but waiting for someone.

542
00:23:58,270 --> 00:23:58,960
Or rather,

543
00:23:59,240 --> 00:24:01,570
waiting for the dragon he had seen before.

544
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:03,840
There are many theories anyway.

545
00:24:08,040 --> 00:24:09,240
Waiting for someone?

546
00:24:23,310 --> 00:24:24,170
Your Highness!

547
00:24:24,770 --> 00:24:25,990
The Sixth Prince's surprise attack
succeeded;

548
00:24:25,990 --> 00:24:27,550
he took the rebels' supply port,

549
00:24:27,550 --> 00:24:28,750
and the rebels
have withdrawn from the capital.

550
00:24:28,750 --> 00:24:29,510
We won!

551
00:24:30,860 --> 00:24:31,970
Where is the Sixth Prince now?

552
00:24:31,970 --> 00:24:32,740
The Sixth Prince

553
00:24:32,740 --> 00:24:34,030
seized the rebels' warships

554
00:24:34,030 --> 00:24:35,270
and is preparing to lead the army north

555
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:36,130
to Tiandu Peak!

556
00:24:37,590 --> 00:24:38,650
Saddle the horses!

557
00:24:41,510 --> 00:24:43,120
You're going to save Yique Yinyang?

558
00:24:43,120 --> 00:24:43,980
Are you insane?

559
00:24:50,200 --> 00:24:51,460
Listen to me carefully!

560
00:24:51,460 --> 00:24:52,960
I've run through this scenario many times.

561
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:54,160
With conventional tactics,

562
00:24:54,160 --> 00:24:55,320
we won't win.

563
00:24:56,210 --> 00:24:57,830
The rebels
have only temporarily withdrawn.

564
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:59,850
Only by seizing this opportunity
to take the port

565
00:24:59,850 --> 00:25:01,270
and send a fleet straight to Tiandu Peak

566
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:02,810
to bring back the Imperial Preceptor

567
00:25:02,810 --> 00:25:04,480
can we turn the situation around.

568
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,830
Otherwise, with our forces as they are,

569
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:07,720
we'll keep losing
no matter how many times we try.

570
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:09,160
Let me tell you what will happen next

571
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:10,460
according to my calculations.

572
00:25:10,460 --> 00:25:11,130
Rebirth Scroll,

